                <note rend="inline" type="source">862.659/6: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Commission to Negotiate Peace</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-08-28T15:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 28, 1919—3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>2978. President has approved that Doctor Charles H. Herty, now Secretary of Board
                    passing on Dye licenses, be sent to Paris as dye expert of the United
                    States.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
